,"myth":false,"baby":false,"eggs":["water1","bug"],"flavor":[{"version":"ruby","text":"MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This POK\u00e9MON flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction - even sideways and backwards - as if it were a helicopter."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"MASQUERAIN\u2019s antennas have eyelike patterns that usually give it an angry look. If the \u201ceyes\u201d are droopy and appear sad, it is said to be a sign that a heavy rainfall is on its way."},{"version":"emerald","text":"It intimidates foes with the large eyelike patterns on its antennae. Because it can\u2019t fly if its wings get wet, it shelters itself from rain under large trees and eaves."},{"version":"firered","text":"The antennae have distinctive patterns that look like eyes. When it rains, they grow heavy, making flight impossible."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"The antennae have distinctive patterns that look like eyes. When it rains, they grow heavy, making flight impossible."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It flaps its four wings to hover and fly freely in any direction-- to and fro and sideways."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It flaps its four wings to hover and fly freely in any direction-- to and fro and sideways."},{"version":"black","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"white","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"x","text":"Its antennae have eye patterns on them. Its four wings enable it to hover and fly in any direction."},{"version":"y","text":"It flaps its four wings to hover and fly freely in any direction--to and fro and sideways."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Masquerain intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This Pok\u00e9mon flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction\u2014even sideways and backwards\u2014as if it were a helicopter."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Masquerain\u2019s antennas have eyelike patterns that usually give it an angry look. If the \u201ceyes\u201d are droopy and appear sad, it is said to be a sign that a heavy rainfall is on its way."},{"version":"sun","text":"It intimidates enemies with the eye-like patterns on its antennae. Its four wings allow it to fly in any direction."},{"version":"moon","text":"Its wings and antennae don\u2019t cope well with moisture. After a rain, it faces sunward to dry off."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Masquerain intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns of its eyespots. If that doesn\u2019t work, it deftly makes its escape on its set of four wings."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its thin, winglike antennae are highly absorbent. It waits out rainy days in tree hollows."}],"evo":{"name":"surskit","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"masquerain","level":1,"min_level":22,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happine